image_analysis.description: This is a legal document titled 'CERTIFICATE OF SERVICE' from a court case. It certifies that a document was served to all counsel and parties of record via electronic filing. The document includes a 'SERVICE LIST' with contact information for attorneys representing different parties. The page is numbered 19 of 19 and has a Bates stamp in the bottom right corner.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header with case information, a centered title, a main body of text, a signature line, a two-column service list, and a footer with a page number and a document identifier.
